parameters: Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Caron-sama, I have returned.

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: 'Caron-sama, I listened to your
lengthy explanation about self-preservation, but can I
conclude that there were no results?'

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: I-I will definitely make up for
it! If you can give me just a little more time, I will
definitely!

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: That's not the important part.
You didn't bring anyone with you to take all the credit for
yourself.

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: Going against the rules of the
Secret Agents is equivalent to betraying Queen Caron.

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: I'll kill you here. Someday, you
will definitely betray the organization for self-
preservation.

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: Eeek!? N-No, that's not it,
it's not trueee!

Queen Caron: Fufu, I appreciate your loyalty, but don't
reduce the number of soldiers unnecessarily by teasing too
much.
Imperial Secret Agent Luid: I went too far.

Queen Caron: I have heard that the 【Staff of Dillark】, which
can manipulate people at will... is certainly convenient,
but it is also a flawed tool.

Queen Caron: It must be the work of that ugly merchant. I
look forward to their fate. I have obtained the main prize,
the 【Demon's Grimoire of Malice, Bral】.

Queen Caron: Now, onto the main topic. It seems that Lex is
seriously opposing us. Our potential allies include the
Senate, nobles, merchants, mercenaries, and various
others...

Queen Caron: Has anyone engaged in battle with the
Adventurer's Guild, who is involved, at all?

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: I have already reported, but we
are currently engaged in battle at the Ishekel's Cage.

Court Magician Eratoma: I have a report. The control is 85%
complete, and I will construct a three-dimensional magic
circle for it. I will return now.

Queen Caron: I see, hahaha, we made it in time. With this,
there are no elements that can make us lose.

Queen Caron: By the way, Emoni, were you about to say
something?

Imperial Secret Agent Emoni: I-I... It's nothing! From now
on, I will pledge absolute loyalty to Queen Caron!

Queen Caron: I am counting on your loyalty. Now then, shall
I have a talk with Atu?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Queen Caron: I see, so Atu has come here.

Queen Caron: Ahahaha, the naive general. It's only natural
for you to side with us if we hold the empire hostage!

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: Everything is in Queen Caron's
hands.

Queen Caron: Luid, let's talk as a parent and child, just
the two of us now. My beloved Luid, my son.
Imperial Secret Agent Luid: Yes, Mother...

Queen Caron: You are the only one I can rely on, the only
one who can protect your weak mother, my son.

Queen Caron: The bond of family, the bond between mother and
child, is something that cannot be denied by anyone, even if
the dark faction and Atu may betray us.

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: The claws of the demon Isheker
are for the sake of the royal family, and Luid's sword
swings only for Mother.
Queen Caron: You are reliable, my beloved son.
Queen Caron: So, are the preparations ready?

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: I appreciate your words, but
such jests...

Queen Caron: I should have made it clear that my decisions
are absolute and not to be questioned, to whom have I given
orders?

Imperial Secret Agent Luid: ...I apologize, I will have
Amina guide you.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
